    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but i'm really worried about hypoglycemia if i take it. since it's just basal, it's meant to cover the background stuff right? if i didn't eat enough to trigger a big spike, wouldn't it be safer to just skip it tonight so i don't wake up with really low blood sugar? it seems like common sense to skip it if there's no food to process.",
